headline: Gold Swings And Fed Jitters Reframe Newmont’s Risk And Reward Profile
summary: Gold prices recently broke all time highs, lifting attention on NYSE:NEM and other major miners. A sharp reversal followed after expectations grew that Kevin Warsh could become the next Federal Reserve chair. The policy signal coincided with a selloff in gold and precious metals equities, highlighting how quickly sentiment can shift.
